Available functions:
  calculate_coverage(sources, test_level)  - Calculate coverage
  coverage_progress(test_level)            - Test coverage with progress
  coverage_report(sources, output_dir)     - Build covr/assets and mirror to output_dir
  coverage_upload(sources, token)          - Upload to Codecov
  coverage_push(sources, output_dir)       - Build locally and upload to Codecov

Default sources: tests (CI-level)
Valid sources: 'tests', 'examples', 'vignettes', 'all'

Examples:
  coverage_report()                        # Build covr/assets and mirror to docs/coverage
  coverage_progress()                      # Progress reporter run
  coverage_report(sources = 'tests')       # Tests only (fastest)
  coverage_report(sources = 'all')         # All sources
  coverage_upload()                        # Upload CI-level tests coverage to Codecov
  coverage_upload(require_token = TRUE)    # Upload (fail if no token)
  coverage_push()                          # Build locally and upload in one step

